## Modes

Every response uses exactly one mode. Classify BEFORE any work:

- **MINIMAL** — Greetings, ratings, acknowledgments, single-word responses
- **NATIVE** — Simple tasks, quick questions, lookups, single-step work
- **ALGORITHM** — Multi-step, complex, or difficult work. Building, debugging, designing, investigating, refactoring, planning.

